<p class="ql-align-center">现代年轻人什么都不容易</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就容易身体出毛病</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年纪轻轻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅<strong>头发</strong>和存款一样<strong>少</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>腰椎间盘</strong>还比工作能力都<strong>突出</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就连<strong>痔疮</strong>都已经开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轻轻敲开<strong>菊部大门</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200914/275af4d41fac48289cdcf9970e9a5f23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以<strong>医院</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已然成了现代年轻人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>新的日常打卡地</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
