<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">只是那些网上怼天怼地怼空气的<strong>弄潮鹅们</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每次一见医生就秒成乖宝宝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只会说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“嗯，对，好的”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不敢怒不敢言更不敢问</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真的卑微</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200914/88e00027a2d64006acde6f97777e63ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可是爱卿们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医院也通<strong>5G网</strong>的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在的医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>上知段子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>下懂暗示</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200914/4ae8cbe0b63841daae28aa2360a7cd40.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你永远猜不到表面正正经经的他们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下一秒会说出什么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了缓解大家的看病心理压力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天朕就带你品味一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不会怼人的段子手</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不是好医生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200914/9839cb93d95c46cb9dba87e62375c9ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医院的“常客”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫过于<strong>孕妇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现代虽说是男女平等了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却依旧避免不了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的人还有着<strong>皇位有人要继承</strong>的思想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重男轻女</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200914/53bee19e1f5a47de94bfcbf3269fd88d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了避免有人堕掉女胎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">政策上明确规定了<strong>禁止胎儿性别鉴定</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以直接问性别？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很有可能只收到<strong>四个字</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200914/807a6761a1504dc89c31f23aaa7a014f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">规矩是死的人是活的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一切压根难不倒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>求知欲旺盛</strong>的家长们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们很好的运用了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老祖宗留下的优秀传统</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们<strong>含蓄委婉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200914/6b199dafae704f119c7d9337f98d4ffb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们<strong>柔弱无助</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200914/d002cdb1932b4f01843aca332c6a2f0e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们<strong>旁敲侧击</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200914/5daee09617d14f1c982a976a3be25a20.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们<strong>欲擒故纵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200914/1e3cecdcb662457d926cf400b32cde6c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然有时你可能遇见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>严</strong>（假）<strong>厉</strong>（装）<strong>警</strong>（很）<strong>告</strong>（凶）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但一定要注意接下来的那一句</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">指不定就有着满满的信息量</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200914/00988514ca6840d58a20e30c2af17fe2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以上情况纯属巧合</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如有雷同</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那抓紧时间买彩票</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别浪费运气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不建议照抄答案套路医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">失败的可能性高达<strong>99%</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟不可鉴定性别是国家实打实的硬性规定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生压力也很大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200914/5c07e4821a834ee4ba797b4dfa8cc4fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而你们这<strong>暗示的技巧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生们也<strong>早已熟练掌握</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就差合适的场合以及人选</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来实操看看了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你瞧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打东边走来的这个女孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是不是就是个暗示的好对象</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200914/f0a8e2d20012429594ff853e86b8cedd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而为了缓解患者的看病压力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生有时候对病情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也会有些许的<strong>委婉暗示</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200914/180a631c10f947e7bded31937949253c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然你可能没救了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但往好处想想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这也算以另一种方式的留名青史了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是不是突然就开心点了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200914/ca83f9976a474746963738cf956e3eec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200914/2385e1d51eae4fb9952dccfb940d26fa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现代年轻人看病</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算心里有再多疑惑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说出来的也只有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“噢，好的，懂了，谢谢医生”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实你只管大胆的问就好了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生什么样的<strong>患</strong>（智）<strong>者</strong>（障）没见过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有专业素养的他们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不会轻易笑场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除非真的忍不住</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200914/42444aa3243a4ac9ab27ff7cc74c46fe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只不过说真的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有些与个人健康<strong>无关</strong>的问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就不要多问了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为问下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伤心的只有你自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200914/6cf91861ddc644a7a52e37e8d0cdc8cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在看病的时候被医生认出了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不要立刻心里暗爽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">觉得自己长相出众让人印象深刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后兴高采烈地问医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎么还记得自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为你以为的答案</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和医生的回答</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可能<strong>差了一个火星那么远</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200914/7bcaf18c68a44859b155236e3e4cfc76.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>好看的皮囊千篇一律</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>优秀的屁股只此一粒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">犹记当年某痔疮帖子里的小伙子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为<strong>屁股翘</strong>火遍了整个医院</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">护士见他都亲昵的称呼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“那个屁股翘的”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对比这个还是该高兴一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至少医生还没把你屁股翘这事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">分享给更多别的同事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200914/ff2cfc5a69d64114a6d885b32ec63e16.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而被爸妈带去看医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一定是不少人的童年阴影</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为你压根不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在家长问了问题后</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自己将面对的是什么</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200914/11fd7ec80eab4cbeb61ffed6c1ce2678.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200914/cec8f2c460bd4079a31184375093cff2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200914/5014c4b1cb3847209deb68599cbe301d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现代人网上怼人<strong>一套接一套</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被医生问个话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就能大脑当场<strong>死机</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时候自己说了些啥都不知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朋友你们就只是看个病而已</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>脑子要当机的这么彻底吗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200914/10fe87763a084d709912610a89ab16ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生看得病得有多少</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才能在面对这些回答的时候不笑出声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过讲真</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这级别的回答都算是轻的了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顶多算是大脑卡了而已</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的回答</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真的会让你怀疑他是不是<strong>大脑中毒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200914/72f1b534f1414b71aaceced7bf8e4f6f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200914/758493ecbbbf4cdebf338d107b47000b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了大脑卡机中毒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的人还会出现被洗脑现象</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生可能也没想过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己普通的一句回答</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">竟然引出了一段<strong>激情喊麦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200914/dc693730637a4b96adf31185d59c1424.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这事儿也不能全怪他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟这种洗脑旋律听过一次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脑子就死活也忘不掉了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不然你们以为“洗脑神曲”是白叫的吗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目前最有效的治疗手段只有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>等下一首洗脑歌曲来覆盖它</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200914/f22a324b049f430f855365ceb1aeb533.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200914/3b2ed821f5f947239c01a05f8b9d5ff5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看病嘛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无论大小总归还是紧张的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟有时候小问题一查</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">指不定就出了什么毛病</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每当这时候就特别希望</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有个人能稍微<strong>安抚一下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在你身边的医生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无疑是<strong>第一人选</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是......</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200914/94374c7345494a4e9bfe41d02ddedd1b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朕查了查这首歌叫<strong>《杀猪刀》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不得不说医生非常的有品位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在提醒患者自己正在一刀刀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>精准切割认真工作</strong>的同时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">配合<strong>欢快而简单的旋律</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抚平人紧张的情绪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>甚至忍不住一起唱起来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200914/a3a285a241264ecc9367773007daaf02.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小时候的你一定被家人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用各种方式<strong>骗过喝药</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们用<strong>糖</strong>诱惑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“喝完就能吃糖”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用<strong>谎言</strong>迷惑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“不苦，你看我都喝了”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至用<strong>旺仔牛奶伪装</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200914/1deee6e95ee44d83aa9cf982c91d2963.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本以为成年后就不会再被骗了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没想到去了医院</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就受到了医生回味童年般的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“ 关 怀 ”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200914/15cfea34baf240208d28982f74bf6093.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这招可谓是<strong>百试百灵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凡事只要先答应下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">具体怎么做</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">医生自有安排</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200914/c4b87fcfc2c64814ad02ac71af861e3e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在孕妇生孩子的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每个医生都化身<strong>打call小能手</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在你身旁不停鼓舞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“加油，快了，你是最棒的，再用力”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时候用力出来的不一定是孩子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有可能是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>屎</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200914/e1a6c603d813422d9ca9dd14ad07606a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然你是真的尴尬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但在医生眼中这也真的是家常便饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孕妇在分娩时的各种<strong>名场面</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们什么没见过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过是拉个屎而已</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">擦一擦又能继续打call了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200914/57b78ea743ed412789a96c9ea170437c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看完了这些名场面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你对看医生的恐惧感是不是有<strong>降低</strong>呢</p>
